originalText.text: This is an excellent stringed instrument rental company. I highly recommend for parents looking for good violins, violas, etc for their musician children.

originalText.text: I had an emergency this morning to find a cello for my daughter who is performing with an orchestra. I am from out of town so that makes it even more challenging but New York Quality Strings' website streamlined the find and connecting with Elliot was a blessing. In less than an hour, he urgently prepared an incredible cello and welcomed me with a warm wide smile and understanding. THANK YOU so much, Elliot and team!!

originalText.text:
I have been renting my daughter's cello from New York Quality Strings (Eliot) for the past 4 years.  Our cello teacher highly recommended Eliot because he took great care of other students.  We obviously loved the interaction.  We have upgraded the size twice, changed additional two times due to damage ( NYC subway) and finally purchased a full size today.   Also changed a bag, bow, one of the strings in the past...  Every interaction for the past 4 years has been positive.   As for the instruments offered,  (tried both basic model and an upgraded one), they are excellent in quality and value.  I am only a high school orchestra level person but the cello that my daughter plays sounds much better than some of other cellos we have used in other venues and while looking around for the final purchase.
I will definitely return to Eliot for future purchases and upgrades.

originalText.text: I had an excellent experience renting a full size, quality-category violin for 3 months. Elliot is wonderful, responds quickly to my questions via email and arranges for me to receive the instrument the very same day I placed my order. Returning the instrument was just as easy. The violin is well made and has a warm lovely sound. I highly recommend this place to anyone looking to rent an instrument!

originalText.text: After some comparison shopping, I began renting a cello from NY Quality strings a few years ago.  It has been such a pleasure to work with Elliot; he responds quickly to any questions,  the instruments are in great condition and I've been able to change instruments easily (size issue).  He was also great in helping me finally purchase a cello.  Highly recommended!
